videos.headline: Georgia takes early lead on 5-yard TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Mecole Hardman in the end zone to give Georgia an early lead over Middle Tennessee.

videos.headline: Holyfield breaks free for 66-yard run
videos.description: Georgia's Elijah Holyfield, son of boxing legend Evander Holyfield, finds a hole for a 66-yard run.

videos.headline: Fromm connects with Holloman for Georgia TD
videos.description: Georgia goes to play-action and QB Jake Fromm finds Jeremiah Holloman in the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Simmons fends off defenders for 56-yard Georgia TD
videos.description: Tyler Simmons stiff-arms a defender and makes his way down the sideline for a 56-yard score.

videos.headline: Georgia's defense recovers fumble
videos.description: Deandre Baker pops the ball loose from Middle Tennessee WR Brad Anderson, and Georgia recovers the fumble.

videos.headline: Georgia turns on the jets for 70-yard punt return TD
videos.description: Mecole Hardman fields the punt and takes it 70 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Middle Tennessee gets on the board with 41-yard TD
videos.description: Brent Stockstill throws a quick pass to Patrick Smith, who gets some help from his blockers on a 41-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Fromm airs it out for 65-yard gain
videos.description: Jake Fromm shows off his arm and puts Georgia in great field position with a long pass to Jeremiah Holloman.

videos.headline: Georgia's Ridley hauls in TD along sideline
videos.description: Riley Ridley gets a foot inbounds as he catches Jake Fromm's 3rd touchdown pass of the day.

videos.headline: Georgia backup QB rushes for 1st TD
videos.description: Georgia QB Justin Fields shows patience and makes a defender miss as he runs for a 15-yard touchdown before halftime.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' offense continues to click in second half
videos.description: Georgia pads its lead as Justin Fields finds Jayson Stanley in the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown.
